--------2017-07-28


Building instructions:
    The CMakeLists.txt provided with this minimal version (2017-07-28) is 
more or less a direct copy from the standalone Astaroth and is not modified to
compile object files only. Therefore the compilation fails if there's no main()
function in gpu_astaroth_new.cc. Hypothetically the project could be built with
"mkdir build && cd build && cmake .. && make -j" once this is fixed.



Also for future reference to whom it may concern.

